---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import TrustedBy from '../components/TrustedBy.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Catering Surrey BC | Indian Catering for Weddings, Corporate Events"
	description="Indian catering Surrey BC for weddings, corporate events, and private parties. Halal, vegan, vegetarian. Award-winning since 2010. Delivery across all Surrey neighbourhoods."
	canonical="/catering-surrey"
>

	<Fragment slot="schema">
		<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
			"@context": "https://schema.org","@type": "Service",
			"name": "Catering Surrey",
			"provider": {"@id": "https://sulacatering.com/#organization"},
			"areaServed": {"@type": "City", "name": "Surrey"},
			"serviceType": "Indian Catering"
		})} />
	</Fragment>

	<section class="hero" style="background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(20,8,16,0.85) 0%, rgba(38,14,38,0.7) 50%, rgba(20,8,16,0.9) 100%), url('https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Indian-food-catering-vancouver-burnaby-richmond.webp');">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<h1>Catering<br/>in <em>Surrey</em></h1>
			<p class="hero-tagline">Indian catering across Surrey, Newton, Guildford, Cloverdale, South Surrey, Whalley. Award-winning since 2010.</p>
			<a href="https://sulaindianrestaurant.com/sula-catering/" class="btn btn-gold">Request Surrey Catering</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="intro-block reveal">
				<h2>Indian Catering for <em>Surrey Events</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
				<p>Surrey is home to one of the largest South Asian communities in Canada, and we honour that with menus that taste like home. From weddings at Grand Taj and Aria to home Diwali celebrations in Newton, from corporate events in Guildford to housewarmings in South Surrey, <a href="/" class="body-link">Sula Catering</a> brings authentic North Indian, South Indian, Hyderabadi, and Goan cuisine to every Surrey event.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Indian-food-catering-vancouver-bc-canada.webp" alt="Indian catering Surrey BC" class="full-width-image" loading="lazy" />

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow">What We Cater in Surrey</p>
				<h2 class="mag-title">Every <em>Surrey Event</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
			</div>
			<div class="service-grid-v2">
				<a href="/weddings" class="service-card-v2 reveal">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/WEDDING.jpg" alt="Wedding catering Surrey" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Surrey Weddings</span>
							<h3>Wedding <em>Catering</em></h3>
							<p>South Asian weddings at Grand Taj, Aria, and home venues across Surrey. Halal, vegetarian, vegan, Jain.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Weddings →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/corporate" class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-100">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/office-catering-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Corporate catering Surrey" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Guildford · Cloverdale</span>
							<h3>Corporate <em>Catering</em></h3>
							<p>Office lunches and conference catering for Surrey's tech parks and corporate buildings.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Corporate →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/private-parties" class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-200">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/indian-catering-vancouver-for-private-parties-birthdays-celebrations.webp" alt="Private party Surrey" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Newton · South Surrey</span>
							<h3>Private <em>Parties</em></h3>
							<p>Birthdays, anniversaries, Diwali, housewarmings, at homes across every Surrey neighbourhood.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Private →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/cafe-catering" class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-300">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="https://sulacafe.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/sula-cafe-near-me-vancouver.webp" alt="Cafe catering Surrey" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Chai · Coffee · Pastries</span>
							<h3>Café <em>Catering</em></h3>
							<p>Live masala chai bars and specialty coffee for Surrey weddings, conferences, brunches.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Café →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-plum">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="experience">
				<div class="experience-img reveal-left">
					<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/weddinf-catering-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Surrey catering" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
				<div class="experience-content reveal-right">
					<h2>We Know <em>Surrey</em></h2>
					<p>Catering Surrey events isn't just about delivering food, it's about delivering the right food. Our menus are built with deep respect for South Asian dining traditions: pure-vegetarian preparation areas, Jain-friendly options, halal-certified meats, and the regional dishes that resonate with extended family gatherings.</p>
					<p>For larger Surrey weddings of 300+, we coordinate directly with venue managers and decor vendors. We also cater across <a href="/catering-vancouver" class="body-link">Vancouver</a>, <a href="/catering-burnaby" class="body-link">Burnaby</a>, and <a href="/catering-richmond" class="body-link">Richmond</a>.</p>
					<div class="experience-stats">
						<div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">500+</div><div class="stat-label">Max Capacity</div></div>
						<div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">$5</div><div class="stat-label">Flat Delivery</div></div>
						<div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">2010</div><div class="stat-label">Established</div></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow">Common Questions</p>
				<h2 class="mag-title">Surrey Catering <em>FAQs</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
			</div>
			<div class="faq-list">
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>Do you cater Surrey wedding banquet halls?</h3><p>Yes, Grand Taj, Aria, and most major Surrey banquet halls. We coordinate with venue managers on setup and timeline.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>How fast is delivery to Surrey?</h3><p>Delivery to Surrey runs 35–45 minutes from our Vancouver kitchens, depending on traffic. Temperature-controlled transport keeps food hot.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>Can you cater large Surrey weddings of 500+ guests?</h3><p>Yes, we regularly cater large South Asian weddings, with experienced staff for large-format service.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>Is Surrey delivery extra?</h3><p>$5 flat delivery, no minimum order, same as Vancouver.</p></div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<TrustedBy />

	<section class="cta-section">
		<div class="reveal">
			<h2>Catering for <em>Surrey</em></h2>
			<p>Tell us your venue, your headcount, your timeline.</p>
			<a href="https://sulaindianrestaurant.com/sula-catering/" class="btn btn-gold">Request a Quote</a>
		</div>
	</section>

</Layout>
